build for javascript backend
database is local memory


create a Contacts table:
  name, required
  email, required
  phone
  company


when user calls GET /api/contacts:
  contacts = get all Contacts
  send back contacts


when user calls POST /api/contacts sending contact:
  saved = save contact to Contacts
  send back saved


when user calls DELETE /api/contacts/:id:
  requires auth
  remove from Contacts with this id
  send back 'deleted'